<doc f='codebrowser/sys/linux/glimp.cpp' l='242'>/*
** XErrorHandler
**   the default X error handler exits the application
**   I found out that on some hosts some operations would raise X errors (GLXUnsupportedPrivateRequest)
**   but those don&apos;t seem to be fatal .. so the default would be to just ignore them
**   our implementation mimics the default handler behaviour (not completely cause I&apos;m lazy)
*/</doc>
